<title>USA: AMEX closing averages.</title>
<headline>AMEX closing averages.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-12</dateline>
<text>
<p>Prices on the American Stock Exchange closed higher in active trading.</p>
<p>The Amex Composite index closed at 626.12, a record, up 3.45.</p>
<p>The average price per share rose $0.08.</p>
<p>Advancers beat decliners 296 to 245.</p>
<p>Preliminary volume was 21,407,500 compared with 19,931,790 on Wednesday.</p>
<p>(Prices official as of 1630 EST/2130 GMT)</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1881))</p>
